<CELL COLS="3">Dol. 155</CELL>
</ROW>
<ROW>
<CELL>Building a comfortable neat timber hou&s;e, out-hou&s;es and negro hutts on this land, will co&s;t about</CELL>
<CELL>&nbsp;</CELL>
<CELL>&nbsp;</CELL>
<CELL>250</CELL>
</ROW>
<ROW>
<CELL>Maintenance of the planter and his family for 4 months, during which time all the above bu&s;ine&s;s may be done and the hou&s;e at lea&s;t rendered habit|able, the expence of travelling to Pen|&s;acola and back to Mi&s;&s;i&s;&s;ippi included</CELL>
