<ROW>
<CELL COLS="3">Deduct the&s;e</CELL>
<CELL>555</CELL>
</ROW>
<ROW>
<CELL COLS="3">from</CELL>
<CELL>900</CELL>
</ROW>
<ROW>
<CELL>and we will leave him now in po&s;&s;e&s;|&s;ion of his land, hou&s;e, two negroes, and ca&s;h to the amount of</CELL>
<CELL>&nbsp;</CELL>
<CELL>&nbsp;</CELL>
<CELL>345</CELL>
</ROW>
