<CELL>&nbsp;</CELL>
<CELL>brought over, 290 D.</CELL>
</ROW>
<ROW>
<CELL>I will &s;uppo&s;e the plantation tools he wants may amount to</CELL>
<CELL>25</CELL>
</ROW>
