<CELL>&nbsp;</CELL>
<CELL>remains 265 D.</CELL>
</ROW>
<ROW>
<CELL>The expences attending a &s;urvey of 400 acres of land (150 miles from the &s;urveyors hou&s;e,) the quantity this family was formerly intitled to, are as follows, viz.</CELL>
<CELL>&nbsp;</CELL>
</ROW>
