<CELL>Surveying 400 acres at 4<ABBR><HI>&s;</HI></ABBR>6</CELL>
<CELL>18</CELL>
</ROW>
<ROW>
<CELL>Milage</CELL>
<CELL>2 3 10</CELL>
</ROW>
<ROW>
<CELL>Allow the &s;urveyor 12 days with four men, but at the &s;ame time the planter may be &s;uppo&s;ed to have a &s;on, being an able lad, who together with the negro make out three, thus remains only one to pay 2<ABBR><HI>&s;</HI></ABBR>6 <HI>per diem,</HI></CELL>
<CELL>1 10 0</CELL>
